=================
INSTALATION NOTES
=================




########
BUILDING
########

You need g++ (= gcc-c++), GNU make and a terminal while compiling source code. Just enter the
main folder and type `./configure' (this checks if you have all the requirements).
Then if you fulfilled our requirements just type `make'. Since now, you can run it directly (`./dungeon-xrawler')
or use some of the shortcuts (like `dungeon-xrawler.desktop').

NOTE: If you want your language translation, install `lokalize' tool before configuring.




#######
WINDOWS
#######

For Windows you can just download the installer [WorkInProgress]



####
MORE
####

More info can be found on wiki:
